OL,5,G1800 Indian Ocean with Simon Reeve
OL,6,     FMadagascar to the Seychelles:
OL,7,     FSimon's journey takes him
OL,8,     Fspearfishing in Madagascar,
OL,9,     Fthrough the slums of Mauritius and
OL,10,     Fon to the Seychelles, where he
OL,11,     Fvisits the world's smallest
OL,12,     Fnational park.
OL,13,G1900 Indian Ocean with Simon Reeve
OL,14,     FKenya to Somaliland: The
OL,15,     Fadventurer travels from the south
OL,16,     Fof Kenya to the Horn of Africa,
OL,17,     Falong the way joining a Ugandan
OL,18,     Fpeace-keeping force in Mogadishu,
OL,19,     Fthe capital of war-torn Somalia.
