OL,5,G2200 Train Truckers
OL,6,     FRoyal Highland Fusilier: The Royal
OL,7,     FHighland Fusilier, a 100-ton
OL,8,     FDeltic diesel engine, must be
OL,9,     Fhauled from Leicestershire to
OL,10,     FWirksworth in Cheshire.
OL,11,G2300 Bangers & Cash
OL,12,     FCortina/Austin Campervan: As a
OL,13,     Fteenager, all Dave wanted for his
OL,14,     Ffirst car was a 2 litre Ghia
OL,15,     FCortina, and today he's off to
OL,16,     FNottinghamshire to collect just
OL,17,     Fthat, alongside a Mark 1 Capri.
